      "description": "Looking for a dependable daily driver with plenty of character? This vehicle is ready for the road and offers a great entry point for someone who doesn't mind a bit of honest wear! While it shows its age with some cosmetic imperfections and could use a little mechanical TLC down the line, it remains a solid, functional choice for your commuting needs. Grab this opportunity to own a reliable ride at a fantastic value!",
