      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle remains in impeccable showroom condition, having been curated with fastidious attention to detail. Every mechanical system and aesthetic surface reflects a standard of preservation rarely encountered in the secondary market. For the discerning individual who accepts only the superlative, this offering represents an absolute benchmark in its class.",
