    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously gotta see this beauty. It\u2019s in absolutely pristine condition\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken incredible care of it, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that looks and feels brand new, this is definitely the one for you. Drop me a message if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
