    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Offered here is a truly exceptional, museum-quality vehicle that has been preserved in a climate-controlled environment. The exterior features original factory paint with a deep, mirror-like finish, further protected by a multi-layer ceramic coating. There are no chips, swirls, or imperfections to be found. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium leather remains supple with no bolster wear, and the carpets have been protected by heavy-duty mats since day one. Mechanically, this car is flawless, backed by a complete, chronological service history from a single authorized dealer. It drives tightly and quietly, exactly as it did when it first left the showroom floor. Included are both original keys, all factory manuals, and a clean, lien-free title. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or enthusiast to acquire a pristine example that requires absolutely nothing.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
